Package: slogr-agent
Version: 1.0.0
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: Slogr Engineering <eng@slogr.io>
Depends: java-21-amazon-corretto-headless | openjdk-21-jre-headless
Section: net
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://slogr.io
Description: Slogr Network Measurement Agent
 TWAMP-based active network measurement agent for the Slogr monitoring
 platform. Measures RTT, jitter, packet loss, and path topology using
 RFC 5357 TWAMP (Two-Way Active Measurement Protocol).
